author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF- Tokio Marine Holdings buys back 5.3 mln shares for 28.69 bln yen in January
text:
Feb 6(Reuters) - Tokio Marine Holdings Inc
* Says it bought back 5.3 million shares for 28.69 billion yen in total, from Jan. 1 to Jan. 31
* Says this was part of the share repurchase plan announced on Nov. 17, 2017
* Says it accumulatively repurchased 9.9 million shares for 51.73 billion yen in total as of Jan. 31
